agrees.\n235: - Keep grouped business behavior discoverable through precise target endpoints; avoid closing unrelated features only through root/shell/whole-file endpoints.\n236: - Merge source files only when it improves target clarity and still preserves per-feature evidence, tests, and controllable file size.\n237: - Treat mustComplete entries as the current phase's executable row-level task list.\n238: - Use behaviorAudit as the current phase behavior audit; it checks closed critical/high rows for source behavior, target behavior, parity, and verification evidence.\n239: - Use uiContract entries as static-analysis planning aids, not complete UI specifications: preserve listed source-visible screen structure, route/back behavior, actions, state feedback, and visual evidence needs, then re-read source/resources/navigation for UI behavior the static analysis may have missed.\n240: - Do not close the phase while current-phase critical/high entries are open, weakly deferred, or missing evidence.\n241: - For every closed critical/high source feature, record sourceBehavior, targetBehavior, parityLevel, targetEndpoints, and verificationEvidence in source-coverage-matrix.json.\n242: - A build pass alone is not per-feature verification; cite tests, manual/emulator evidence, or explicit verificationEvidence for behavior closure.\n243: - Use implemented-simplified only with concrete simplification reason, preserved-behavior explanation, target endpoints or tests, and source/platform evidence.\n244: - If a suitable HarmonyOS/Cangjie API, Kit, example, or package exists for a platform capability, use it or record a platform replacement; do not close the item with local mock data, sample data, in-memory simulation, or another fallback.\n245: - Use deferred only for concrete blockers; otherwise implement faithfully or platform-replace with evidence.\n246: - Update source-coverage-matrix.json/md and platform-capability-check.json/md before phase completion.\n247: - If this checklist is empty but the phase has real scope in plan.md/plan.json, assign plannedPhase values first.\n\n(End of file - total 247 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Phase Task Checklist\n\n- Phase: `phase-01-project-skeleton-resources`\n\n## Purpose\n\nCurrent-phase task checklist generated from the agent-maintained source coverage matrix and platform capability check. Use it before editing and update the matrix/check after work.\n\n## Summary\n\n| metric | value |\n| --- | --- |\n| phaseFeatureEntries | 18 |\n| phaseCriticalHighFeatureEntries | 18 |\n| mustCompleteFeatureEntries | 18 |\n| needsEvidenceFeatureEntries | 0 |\n| deferredOrFallbackFeatureEntries | 0 |\n| coveredFeatureEntries | 0 |\n| phaseSourceFiles | 5 |\n| phasePlatformCapabilityEntries | 0 |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"translation-inputs\\phase-task-checklist.md","time":{"start":1782362421150,"end":1782362421168}},"id":"prt_efd143794001UJZxpQm9C5lieO","sessionID":"ses_102ebfe8affe4GSHMvbO5MZBl3","messageID":"msg_efd142313001XUJ6Yf5lwaeOyR"}}
